idyllic 

Art book cover complete! Now to sort out logistics... Aiming for release in October, hopefully have some ready for Armageddon and Smash (if it happens ahh I miss my aus friends). I used some photos from a Japanese inn I stayed at to create the background! 

This piece will be available on my patreon for July’s rewards! 

#artistsoninstagram #animeart #animegirl #clipstudiopaint #japan #japanlife #japantravel #digitalillustration
